### Buscar Logs de um Usuário Específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/infraestrutura/auditoria/usuario/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response
# Status: 200 OK
# [
#   {
#     "id": "log-uuid-1",
#     "tipoLog": "ACESSO",
#     "usuarioId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
#     "dataHora": "2024-01-15T14:30:00Z",
#     "acao": "Login",
#     ...
#   },
#   ...
# ]

